BEGIN_PGML
Find both intercepts and the slope of the line.

[`[$left]=[$right]`]

[@KeyboardInstructions('Enter the [`x`]-intercept here.')@]**

[_]{$xi}{5}

[@KeyboardInstructions('Enter the [`y`]-intercept here.')@]**

[_]{$yi}{5}

[@KeyboardInstructions('Enter the slope here.')@]**

[_]{$m}{5}

END_PGML

